product.name: Boho Comforter Set Queen Size Striped Pleats Bohemian Seersucker Bedding Set All Season Soft Cozy 3 Pieces Quilt with 2 Pillowcases(90"X90" Light Blue)
product.description:
To elevate sleep with quality bedding that blends comfort and style.
We draw inspiration from diverse cultures and design styles around the globe. Our bedding products incorporate these influences, blending aesthetics with comfort.
Each item is carefully designed and selected to ensure both visual appeal and comfort. We use high-quality materials and innovative techniques to provide a pleasing experience.
Our bedding is more than just decor; it is an integral part of your personal space. Whether for warmth in winter or coolness in summer, our products aim to create a peaceful sleep.
product.bullet_points:
• Premium Material: Crafted from high-quality microfiber and filled with light and fluffy polyester, ensuring soft cozy, and breathable. It is suitable for all seasons
• Distinctive Design: Features a dual-sided design with elegant and exquisite stripe seersucker on one side (A-side) and 3D knitted bean texture fabric on the other (B-side), which is beautiful and comfortable
• Size Selection: This queen comforter set includes 3 pieces: 1 comforter measuring 90"x90" and 2 pillowcases measuring 20"x26"
• Effortless Cleaning: Our comforter set is machine washable, making care a breeze
• Dedicated Customer Service: please don't hesitate to contact us with any questions about our products
